    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation. While the engine and transmission are solid and perform reliably, the car shows noticeable signs of wear consistent with its age, including some minor exterior scuffs and interior upholstery thinning. It has been well-maintained mechanically to ensure it remains a dependable option for its next owner.",
